<i>bird</i>), 200 gp (<i>fan</i>), 450 gp (<i>swan boat</i>), 400 gp (<i>tree</i>), 500 gp (<i>whip</i>).</p>\n</div>\n    ','SRD 3.5 MagicItemsV');
